x%2Fi%2F3tyBA94.png&h=40739760&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T20:35:54.000Z","msg":"所以永遠咩都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c38e80831abacfe7594cc3dc29d573208ea616","tid":1792844,"uid":320316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T20:42:54.000Z","msg":"一早mute撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前8點屯市唱歌 8點講撚到8點半 8點半講撚到9點半<br />\n跟住啲行動時間永遠啲人只會問 開波未 有冇文具 大隊係邊 多唔多人<br />\n跟住又有幾隊友係度打飛機講廢話 <br />\n個grp冇撚用既 靠呢班人做野真係食得屎<br />\n睇屯哨算撚數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c84b56614b0f87279826af6a40acf4c3fd6fb6","tid":1792844,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T20:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1658492ec9ce88a5c7c0f13d3bc7ddf739708524","tid":1792844,"uid":296294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T21:37:02.000Z","msg":"之前都試過叫人塞屯公<br />\n人影都冇隻<br />\n跟住仲話屯門人係愛好和平既牛牛<br />\nbtw,唔緊要啦，各有各玩"},{"pid":"db75472a56024bc4671deef62a1938a2f245dab6","tid":1792844,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c84b56614b0f87279826af6a40acf4c3fd6fb6","tid":1792844,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T20:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"荃灣都係 根本個個都係咁"},{"pid":"ed97da15d53329d5bbf0151325bb306ab5c3726b","tid":1792844,"uid":140963,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"個個公海都係低質架啦，玩左咁耐仲睇公海做人無野呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n開花快閃既話想做野就同自己team一齊做, 要做野貓單人行動咪自己mon post, Miss左咪爬文囉, 下下公海伸手問人, 有人答你唔係義務<br />\n<br />\n想知有咩大活動咪睇日程表囉<br />\n<br />\n玩左半年仲on99咁"}]}